malizing the volume elements of the various information\nmetrics, is also discussed in our context.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 8 Apr 2005 18:48:05 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 6 May 2005 18:10:29 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 30 Aug 2005 16:10:26 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Mon, 2 Jan 2006 23:03:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-11"}
